CNBC Asia.label: CNBC Asia
CNBC Asia.description: CNBC Asia is a business news television channel in Asia. A subsidiary of NBCUniversal, it is the Asian service of the Consumer News and Business Channel. Wikipedia

CNBC Europe.label: CNBC Europe
CNBC Europe.description: CNBC Europe is a business and financial news television channel which airs across Europe, the Middle East and Africa. The station is based in London, where it shares the Adrian Smith-designed 10 Fleet Place building with Dow Jones & Company. Wikipedia

Canadian Broadcasting Corporation.label: Canadian Broadcasting Corporation

Caracol TV.label: Caracol Television
Caracol TV.description: Caracol Televisión is a Colombian private national television network, owned by the Santo Domingo Group. Wikipedia

Czech Radio.label: Czech Radio
Czech Radio.description: Český rozhlas is the public radio broadcaster of the Czech Republic, and broadcasts throughout the Czech Republic nationally and on 13 regional stations. Wikipedia

Discovery Channel.label: Discovery Channel
Discovery Channel.description: Discovery Channel is an American basic cable and satellite television channel that is the flagship television property of Discovery Communications, a publicly traded company run by CEO David Zaslav. Wikipedia

NHK World.label: NHK World

Nederlandse Omroep Stichting.label: Nederlandse Omroep Stichting
Nederlandse Omroep Stichting.description: The Nederlandse Omroep Stichting, English Netherlands Broadcasting Foundation, is one of the broadcasting organizations making up the Netherlands Public Broadcasting system. Wikipedia

ProSiebenSat.1 Welt.label: ProSiebenSat.1 Welt

Télévision Suisse Romande.description: The Télévision suisse romande was a TV network with two channels RTS Un and RTS Deux. They are the main French language channels in Switzerland, part of SRG SSR. They provide content for TV5MONDE. Wikipedia

TVN (Poland).label: TVN

Telewizja Polska.label: Telewizja Polska

Eurosport.label: Eurosport
